snippet.title: MetaDOS Unique Point: Time⏱
snippet.description:
🔥MetaDOS Unique Point: Time⏱

⚡To speed up the upcoming match, DOS Labs created a completely different time system. The same specific amount of time is given to each participant. It's a countdown time system, if it returns to zero, the player will knockdown.
⚡To survive and become last-man-standing, players need to find an additional time that has been randomly placed by DOS Labs on the most attractive tournament on the planet.
💪An effective time management strategy is necessary for the ultimate survival of the match.

🌐Official Channels: https://ds.gl/go
